@startuml
title Arena Master — Vista Lógica (Capas y Componentes)
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "Frontend Angular" as FE {
  [UI Components\n(Dashboard/Torneos/Encuentros/Tabla/Participantes)] as UI
  [Guards\n(authGuard/roleGuard)] as Guards
  [HTTP Interceptors\n(auth/timeout)] as Interceptors
  [Services\n(Auth/Torneo/Encuentro/Tabla/Participante)] as FEServices
}

package "Backend Spring Boot" as BE {
  [Controllers\n(Auth/Torneo/Participante/Encuentro/Tabla)] as Controllers
  [Services\n(Auth/Torneo/Encuentro/Tabla/Participante)] as Services
  [DTO + Mapper\n(Request/Response)] as DTO
  [Security\n(SecurityConfig/JwtAuthFilter/JwtService)] as Security
  [Repositories\n(JPA)] as Repos
  [Domain Model\n(Torneo/Encuentro/TablaPosiciones/\nParticipantes/Usuario)] as Model
}

database "DB" as DB

UI --> Guards : Control de acceso\npor rutas y roles
UI --> FEServices : Acciones de usuario\n(CRUD/flujo)
FEServices --> Interceptors : Adjunta JWT\ny timeout
Interceptors --> Controllers : REST/JSON

Controllers --> Security : Autorización\n(Spring Security)
Controllers --> Services : Orquestación\nreglas de negocio
Services --> DTO : Mapear Request/Response
Services --> Repos : Persistencia\n(JPA)
Repos --> DB
Services --> Model
Repos --> Model
DTO --> Model
Security --> Services : Carga usuario/roles

note bottom of Services
Reglas principales:
- Iniciar fase de grupos genera encuentros y tabla.
- Registrar resultado actualiza tabla.
- Transiciones de estado del torneo controladas.
end note
@enduml
